      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">About the Creator</h1>
      <p class="py-6">Hi, my name is Rose Soriano. Thank you for trying out my website! I am a software engineer based out of southern California, but I am originally from Texas where I eventually got my degree in Computer Engineering.</p>
      <p class="py-6">I started cubing when I was in elementary school after a classmate had solved a Rubik's cube full of jelly (for lube) in front of the class. Interested in seeing how hard solving one really was, I learned CFOP from YouTube videos. I ultimately fell off of cubing amongst other hobbies as I got older, but I have gotten back into cubing again after graduating from college. I was shocked to find out stickerless cubes are now competition legal! During this time of learning more advanced CFOP techniques, I realized that I struggle to learn with the existing resources out there. From a programmers perspective, I aim to create learning tools that I think provide a more intuitive and efficient user experience.</p>
